==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unhoused
<hw>Un*housed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<ety>[Properly p. p. of <ets>unhouse</ets>.]</ety> <def>Driven from a
house; deprived of shelter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> + <ets>housed</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Not provided with a house or shelter; houseless;
homeless.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unhouseled</ent>⟦br⟧
